text: KFOH-LP (99.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Saint Joseph, Missouri. The station is owned by St. Joseph Music Foundation. It airs a variety format. The station was assigned the KFOH-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on June 9, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FOH-LP FOH-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Missouri Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Buchanan County, Missouri
